Don't want a straightforward single or return? No problem.

Adults

Adult passengers are aged 16 and over.

Young Adults

Young adult passengers aged from 12-15. Young adult passengers travelling alone can't book online - please contact reservations on 0844 209 7777 for help.

Children

Children must be aged 2-11 on the date of their flight.

Infants

Infants don't get their own seat on the plane - they'll need the comfort of your lap.
